<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.9.5">
<l>veṇkalap pattiram kaṭṭi viḷaiyāṭi</l>
<l>kaṇpala ceyta karuntaḻaik kāviṉkīḻ</l>
<l>paṇpala pāṭippal lāṇṭicaip papaṇṭu</l>
<l>maṇpala koṇṭāṉ puṟampulkuvāṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">vāmaṉaṉ eṉṉaip puṟampulkuvāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Wearing a leaf of bronze, playfully [coming] under a forest</l>
<l>of dark peacock feathers made of many eyes</l>
<l>while singing many songs and intoning ‘many years’,</l>
<l>he who took the many worlds of old will embrace [me] from behind.</l>
<l>Vāmana will embrace me from behind.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
